<DATE_TIME> 1999-04-19 00:20 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3653 &Cx1f; tth-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-FBN-SEAHAWKS-SPI &LR;      04-19 0743
