Technology who has studied China's state-owned enterprises. ``This
agreement puts tremendous pressure on China to change its
industrial structure, and to some degree its politics. It will be
painful.
</P>
<P>
   ``And the question is, how can you say that you want a
market-based China, enmeshed in a global legal system, and walk
away from this?''
</P>
<P>
   &QL; 
NYT-04-17-99 1127EDT &QL;
</P>
</TEXT>
