the world's most successful investors, shares some of his secrets
in this interview. Above all, he says, he pays no attention to the
ups and downs of the stock market but focuses instead on individual
companies with good business concepts and sound management.
Buffett, whose investment firm Berkshire Hathaway controls cash
resources of $15 billion, also explains his latest venture : a
