driven on the street, I would scowl, ``Disgusting display of
excess.'' And, yes, a Hummer probably is more vehicle than anyone
really needs. But after a week with my competition yellow civilian
version of the same vehicle that our troops are using around the
world, I came away a fan. (Sharp, Atlanta Jounal-Constitution)
