<SLUG> BC-DIARY-HEATHER20-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Confessions of a diarist: Heather is me
 &HT;    By Omar L. Gallaga
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   AUSTIN, Texas _ ``Writing is supposed to be a kind of
confessional, transmogrified a little, but ultimately the place
where your triumphs of pride and the sins of your past are blended
with fictions.'' _ Heather Yi
</P>
