<P>
   REDS-SPARKY _ The Cincinnati chapter of the Baseball Writers
Association of America will induct former Reds manager George
``Sparky'' Anderson into the Reds Hall of Fame on Friday, July 16
during on-field ceremonies prior to the Reds' game vs the Colorado
Rockies. (McCoy, Dayton Daily News).
</P>
