</P>
<P>
   BASKETBALL
</P>
<P>
   BKN-HAWKS _ Nine games left in this bizarre season, and the
Hawks still have no idea where they will finish in the Eastern
Conference and what their playoff goals are. Injury and illness
have hampered them recently, but other teams are affected, too.
They win close games and beat good teams but lose to inferior ones.
A look ahead, beginning with Toronto on Tuesday. (Denberg, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution).
</P>
