of contemporary art presented regularly. And, even though the next
Whitney Biennial doesn't open until 2000, it's already a hot topic.
That's because the artists for the 2000 Whitney Biennial Exhibition
will be chosen by six curators from outside New York City _
including Michael Auping, chief curator for the Modern Art Museum
of Fort Worth. By JANET TYSON. Story has moved in ``e''
entertainment category. &QL; 
