<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    WINDOWS 98 GETTING HOME COMPUTER NETWORK FEATURE
 &HT;    Moving in (f) financial and (w) Washington categories
 &HT;    By ANDREW J. GLASS
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
