<DOCTYPE> MISCELLANEOUS TEXT (slug-filter) </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-04-19 19:57 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4848 &Cx1f; taf-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-FINFRONTS-NYT &LR;      04-19 0446
