<HEADLINE>
CLINTON SEEKS $6 BILLION TO PAY FOR WAR 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (i and w coding)   (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  
 By FRED KAPLAN  
 c.1999 The Boston Globe  
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON _ Inside President Clinton's request Monday for $6
billion in emergency funds to pay for the war in Yugoslavia lies a
