its T2000 probably has a better home video, audio and computer
system than your house, and a better security-surveillance system.
But Kenworth's truck is loaded with some serious-minded technology,
like cameras that give the driver a view of the blind spot along
the right side of the trailer.
</P>
<P>
   By Bill Virgin. (Story has moved in the ``f'' category.)
