posed any danger to the president (except, perhaps, the woman who
woman  &LR; emerged in her bathrobe). Meanwhile,  &UR; Jane Mazarella &LR;  is
wondering if those snazzily uniformed guys who parked their car
next to a fire hydrant near the hotel for at least five hours were
