<HEADLINE>
REMOVE THE SILENCER ON GUNS 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
 By E.J. MONTINI  
 c.1999 The Arizona Republic  
<TEXT>
<P>
   PHOENIX _ Two police officers shot dead within 22 days and the
news is filled with stories about violence and lawlessness and lack
of values and urban expansion and Hollywood irresponsibility and
everything except what counts _ guns.
</P>
