</P>
<P>
   I don't know if Susan had an opinion on the subject. But at
least her silence, unlike ours, is understandable. &QL; 
E.J. Montini can be reached at (602) 444-8978 or at
ed.montini(at)pni.com via e-mail. &QL;
</P>
